notes.body: Hello Sonu,     Greetings from PharmEasy!    I see that your order #654499139822288896 was assigned for a free consultation with our tie-up doctor. As per the records, your order has been cancelled by our partnered doctor because you have refused for a teleconsultation. I am sorry for the inconvenience caused to you.     Please be informed that we are unable to process your order without completing a teleconsultation or a valid prescription. Our doctor can connect with you via a normal call using either the registered number or the delivery number provided. Unfortunately, teleconsultation via email is not available at this time.   I request you to place a new order with a valid prescription to avoid doctor consultation. You can also opt for a free consultation at the time of placing the order. Also, I request you to kindly get back to us if the doctor has cancelled the order wrongly.   You may visit the link mentioned below for clarification.  https://pharmeasy.in/help/doctor-consultation-43000550954/why-was-a-doctor-consultation-arranged-for-my-order--43000487599     I see the refund of Rs. 3303.92 was initiated on 29th June 2025. It will be credited to your original payment source within 5 to 7 working days.     Please note: Saturday, Sunday, and public holidays will not be included in business days. Refund timelines depend on Bank turnaround times. I appreciate your patience and understanding in the meantime.  For any further assistance, please reopen this ticket or reach out to us through our support channels, in the App or website, listed in the 'Need Help' section.     Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Stay healthy!     Regards,  Habiba
notes.body_html:
Hello Sonu,

Greetings from PharmEasy!

I see that your order #654499139822288896 was assigned for a free consultation with our tie-up doctor. As per the records, your order has been cancelled by our partnered doctor because you have refused for a teleconsultation. I am sorry for the inconvenience caused to you.

Please be informed that we are unable to process your order without completing a teleconsultation or a valid prescription. Our doctor can connect with you via a normal call using either the registered number or the delivery number provided. Unfortunately, teleconsultation via email is not available at this time.

I request you to place a new order with a valid prescription to avoid doctor consultation. You can also opt for a free consultation at the time of placing the order. Also, I request you to kindly get back to us if the doctor has cancelled the order wrongly.

You may visit the link mentioned below for clarification.
https://pharmeasy.in/help/doctor-consultation-43000550954/why-was-a-doctor-consultation-arranged-for-my-order--43000487599

I see the refund of Rs. 3303.92 was initiated on 29th June 2025. It will be credited to your original payment source within 5 to 7 working days.

Please note: Saturday, Sunday, and public holidays will not be included in business days. Refund timelines depend on Bank turnaround times. I appreciate your patience and understanding in the meantime.

For any further assistance, please reopen this ticket or reach out to us through our support channels, in the App or website, listed in the 'Need Help' section.

Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Stay healthy!

Regards,
Habiba

      Subject: Request for Refund Due to Delayed Delivery and Extra COD charges .  
      Description:  Dear Sir / madam  I would like to bring to your attention the issues I faced with my recent pharmeasy order. The 
 delivery was made after the scheduled date, and additionally , I was charged extra at the time of cash on Delivery , which was not mentioned during the order placement process .  
   
 The order details are as follows- 
 1)  ORDER ID - 653307221534023680-58848 
 2)DATE OF ORDER - 28 NOVEMBER  
 3) EXPECTED DELIVERY - 28 NOVEMBER  
 4)ACTUAL DELIVERY DATE - 30 NOVEMBER 
 5)AMOUNT COLLECTED ON DELIVERY 774 /- INSTEAD OF 717/- 
   
 Due to the delay in delivery , I had difficulty obtaining essential medicines on time , which caused unnecessary inconvenience, Furthermore , the extra charges collected during COD were unexpected and unacceptable.  
   
 Therefore , I request you to  
 1- compensate for the delay in delivery by refunding the medicine amount or giving suitable resolution as per policy .

helpdesk_ticket.description:
Dear friends
I placed above order for two packs of One touch verio test strips, 50
strips each and received these on  19/11/2025.
I opened one box yesterday to measure the  diabetes  before dinner and the
reading showed "LO". I measured it again two hours  after dinner and again
it showed "LO".
I was very much worried and I fed the patient the sugary substances and
sugary drinks but even after that again the reading was "LO". I measured
the reading on another healthy person and again the reading was "LO". After
this I opened second box and measured the reading. It was 218 and at the
same time the reading from the first box showed only 20.
It means the content of one box is either fake or defective. It caused me a
lot of anxiety and worry.
I registered the complaint under ticket no. 22227793 but you closed it
prematurely without waiting for my response. I am enclosing all the photos
required by you and also enclosing the readings recorded on one touch
applications for your action
. please arrange to return this packet as it is either fake or defective.
Thanks
Rajkumar Goel

--

Hej, 
 Erbjuder ni tjänster eller produkter till fastighetsbolag? 
 Ni kan skicka epost reklam precis som detta till fastighetsbolag i hela Sverige. 
 Eftersom du läser detta mail så vet du att reklam utskick via epost fungerar. 
 Vi har hjälpt hundratals företagare att få nya kunder, alltifrån städfirmor till säkerhetsbolag och nu vill vi hjälpa ännu fler. 
 Läs mer om vad andra företag tycker om oss här: https://www.fastighetslistor.se/kundomdomen 
 Nyligen hjälpte vi en städfirma att få 22 offertförfrågningar redan inom 24 timmar. 
 Vi hjälper er att komma i kontakt med tusentals fastighetsbolag. Antingen i ert län, i flera län eller i hela Sverige. 
 Nu kan ni köpa Fastighetslistor med kontaktinformation till alla fastighetsbolag i Sverige. 
 Fastighetslistor innehåller följande information: - Företagsnamn - E-postadress - Hemsida - Telefon - Adress - Kommun 
 All kontaktinformation ni behöver för att nå ut till nya kunder ingår i våra excel listor. 
 Med tanke på hur dyrt det är med frimärken så sparar ni både tid och pengar, samt får resultat mycket snabbare via epost. Det bästa är att ni äger listorna för livet, inga bindningstider eller konstiga abonnemang. 
 Eftersom vi nyss lanserat Fastighetslistor så har vi ett erbjudande. 
 Istället för ordinarie pris på 5 Kr per fastighetsbolag med epostadress tar vi nu endast 2 Kr per epostadress. Minimum beställning på 3,000 st fastighetsbolag gäller för att få rabatterade priset på 2 kr styck. 
 Erbjudandet gäller endast fram till Fredag 5 December 2025. 
 Ni kan se antal fastighetsbolag samt priser här: https://www.fastighetslistor.se/priser 
 Det är väldigt enkelt att beställa kontaktinformation till fastighetsbolag från oss, på beställningsformuläret fyller ni bara i alla områden ni vill ha listor i. 
 Kom ihåg att erbjudandet på endast 2 Kr styck per fastighetsbolag med epostadress gäller endast fram till Fredag 5 December 2025. 
 Fastighetslistorna levereras i excel format och är engångskostnad. 
 Ni är välkomna att kontakta oss vid eventuella frågor och funderingar. 
 Med vänliga hälsningar, Mehmet Aksoy Telefon: 070-488 05 43 https://www.Fastighetslistor.se

Hi Team,

I assumed PharmEasy delivers orders on time like Apollo and Tata 1mg.
Unfortunately, my order was delayed and I did not receive any update from
your side.

I called the delivery person at *9:35 PM* (Number: *7022397342*), and he
clearly said delivery is not possible today and he is not aware of my area.
However, immediately after the call, I received a message saying *“Oops!
Our delivery partner reached your doorstep but couldn’t deliver your order,
we’ll try again tomorrow morning before 10 AM”*.

This is completely misleading and feels like cheating the customer.

Thank you for your service, but I will not be placing any further orders
with PharmEasy.

Regards,
Kirthi Medicals

notes.body: Hello Koteswara,     Greetings from PharmEasy!  We have received an update from our Logistics team that your order has been delivered to you. We hope you have received the same. Due to operational challenges at the courier partner’s end, a delay occurred in the order. The necessary feedback has been shared with the courier partner to serve you better ahead. We apologise for the inconvenience caused to you.     In the future, please contact our Level 1 customer service team via a call to 8071324888 or send an email to care@pharmeasy.in. If your query remains unresolved for 7 days after you have reached out to our Level 1 Customer support, you can escalate the matter to us.     For any further assistance, please reach out to us through our support channels on the app or website listed in the "Need Help" section.  Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Stay Safe.  Regards, Grievance Officer HelpDesk.
